# Envelope Budgeting

This project is **Envelope Budgeting** — a mobile-friendly personal finance web app.

## Stack
- Next.js App Router, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS
- PostgreSQL on Railway via Prisma
- JWT cookie sessions

## Core features
- Expenses, income, categories, tax-deductible flags
- Monthly budgets vs actuals
- Goals (house, student debt, emergency fund, etc.)
- Insights and CSV export

## Conventions
- Keep the UI simple and mobile-first
- Amounts stored as integer cents in the database
- Do not reset production Railway databases
